    "Deep learning can turn the whole process in an end-to-end manner.",
    "For example, deep learning techniques can directly deal with bug reports and help automate the process of bug report management.• Challenges in high-quality training data acquisition.",
    "The primary challenge faced by most subareas of software engineering is obtaining high-quality training data.",
    "First, the sizes of datasets are often limited.",
    "For example, publicly accessible data for requirements typically are small in volume and lack some details, making it difficult to train effective deep learning models."
